Our Approach:
1. Understand your personal health journey
2. Explore mental, emotional, and lifestyle contributors
3. Re-frame health through empathy, science, and coaching
4. Equip you with guides, tools, and practical steps to untie the knots and regain control
At Dr A Medical Wellness Centre, we believe every lifestyle-related condition has a story.
Behind high blood sugar, high blood pressure, ulcers, fatigue, or other recurring issues,
there are knots of stress, poor habits, emotional strain, or trauma. We do not just manage
symptoms - we teach you what your condition really means, provide practical tools, and
empower you to take charge of your health.
